{"tid":1499561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見好多新用Twitter 嘅巴打話無followers 我有小小建議","createTime":"2019-08-23T18:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T18:14:48.000Z","uid":235495,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"595341ae62b1fc365bf948149dd06074aaf440d2","tid":1499561,"uid":235495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:09:22.000Z","msg":"1. Twitter 最大嘅特點係 個個都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好隨意就follow人+搭嗲</span></span></span> follow 完某啲ac佢會有suggestions 我覺得佢啲suggestion 係幾好 可以一路跟住follow <br />\n<br />\n2. 撳入某啲hashtag 例如: #eye4hk # freeHongKong 之類 其實有大量同路人 甚至外國人 只要你follow完 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對方見你係同路人 自然會互追</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 承上題，撳入去 除咗follow人 仲可以comment 甚至做文宣。唔使驚三唔識七 人哋唔睬你 Twitter 就係一個可以隨便搭嗲嘅地方。 對方都係對嘅事香港有關心，先會用相關hashtag  。所以要用你自己最<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真實嘅感情同文字</span></span>去講俾外面啲人知香港發生咩事。唔好一嚟就spam 人。可以tag其他人但通常Twitter 文化唔會咁做 用hashtag 居多 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要tag都只會tag一兩個。頂盡真係三個</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4. Follow 啲自己鐘意嘅嘢 再有其興趣嘅人follow 你。你tweet 香港嘅事 佢見到 再retweet 岀去 無限loop <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係我覺得Twitter 非常可取嘅地方。<br />\n不過我認為呢個方法 需要用長時間去建立自己個profile 如果你打算之後都會繼續用Twitter 咪當係你嘅ig fb咁經營都無妨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能講到一舊舊 但真心希望幫到大家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1466778d93fc1b8e75dc0f9b901501a9972c561a","tid":1499561,"uid":235495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0e1ded61cdd3c9dceaa2d7257af3ed837cee72","tid":1499561,"uid":235495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70048743aab246ec95857cf2248146eb6b011b6f","tid":1499561,"uid":235495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9230084a0cba9b60020ad5eef2909fbf9a98ac","tid":1499561,"uid":235495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4ef02119777ad658d826370905594f7f6dadba","tid":1499561,"uid":235495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57698efd19a068f7d299251cd89116977f4afed","tid":1499561,"uid":235495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b2bcef0cb3e257137bc4951092a262506ce266","tid":1499561,"uid":235495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" c